query:
INSERT INTO user_course_instance_exercise_service_variables (
    exercise_service_slug,
    user_id,
    course_instance_id,
    exam_id,
    variable_key,
    variable_value
  )
VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6) ON CONFLICT (
    variable_key,
    user_id,
    course_instance_id,
    exercise_service_slug,
    exam_id,
    deleted_at
  ) DO
UPDATE
SET variable_value = $6;
